Necromancy
Levels: Blackguard 4
Components: V, S
Range: Touch
Target: Creature touched.
Saving Throw: None
Spell Resistance: Yes

<i>Your touch siphons some of the life energy from a creature, leaving a soul-numbing ball of darkness in your grasp.</i>

You must succeed on a melee touch attack against a living creature. If you do so, your touch deals 1d6 points of negative damage per two caster levels (maximum 15d6). 

You regain one use of turn undead on a successful attack.